column5: Hey guys and gals,  The Barrie Bassmasters are holding our annual Fall Challenge on Balsam Lake on September 30th out of the Provincial Park.  Entry fee is $120.00 per team, blastoff at 7:30.  More info is available at www.barriebassmasters.org
Steve Whats the scoop on the Barrie Simcoe tourney? Is it all of Simcoe,or just the bay? Looking forward to that one.
Brian, I'm not sure if its restricted to the bay or not, I'll have to find out.
